    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        "The course curriculum is really good, and the college exams are conducted on a yearly basis. The college is affiliated with Jiwaji University, which is situated in Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh.",
        "I got 8000 for the internship; many companies come here with a good package for students.",
        "The placements were good; many of them went to good companies. It was good advertising. Jobs were more, and small internships were given to people.",
        "Many scholarships are given by the college to those who are domiciled at the college level.",
        "The faculty always helps students, and the students are also good in this college. Thats why I came to this college.",
        "The facilities in hostels are good, but I have never stayed in one. Many people enjoy staying in hostels, although the food may not be proper. Nevertheless, they make their own food to have some fun.",
        "The college has a good, well-stocked library, gymnasium, good computer center, and one of the best sporting systems in Chennai."
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        "After studying this course, students usually go for a Masters degree instead of applying for other jobs, unless any unforeseen circumstances occur.",
        "Our Union party offers free books to very poor families who cannot afford to buy any. We, the Union students, provide this offer.",
        "You have to take a flat nearby or have to stay with friends in a nearby mess.",
        "I dont have any negative remarks about my college because I couldnt find anything bad about it."
      ]
    },
    "affiliated_to": {
      "name": "University of Calcutta, Kolkata"
    }
